OL,9,FCountry singer and actor Kris
OL,10,FKristofferson has died aged 88
OL,11,F"peacefully" and "surrounded by his
OL,12,Ffamily" at his home in Maui, Hawaii, a
OL,13,Frepresentative for the star has said.
